1 KAPPA_Version_1.4

   A new release of KAPPA (v1.4) has been made. The main changes are:

   o The HISTAT and STATS applications now display the position of the
   minimum and maximum pixel values in the current WCS coordinate system
   rather than AXIS coordinates.

 For complete details of all changes, see the "Release Notes" appendix in
 SUN/95.

